            "section": "Introduction",
            "text": "Mucormycosis is an invasive and fatal fungal infection that is caused by Mucorales, an order of zygomycete fungi [1, 2] ."
        },
        {
            "cite_spans": [
                {
                    "end": 288,
                    "ref_id": "BIBREF0",
                    "start": 285,
                    "text": "[1]"
                },
                {
